# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:23
msgid "Learn More"
msgstr "Pelajari Lebih Lanjut"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:24
msgid ""
"We are working hard to expand this user guide and to improve OpenShot Video "
"Editor, but if you are stuck and don't know where to turn, OpenShot has "
"several sources for additional information."
msgstr ""
"Kami bekerja keras untuk mengembangkan panduan pengguna ini dan meningkatkan "
"OpenShot Video Editor, tetapi jika Anda mengalami kesulitan dan tidak tahu "
"harus ke mana, OpenShot memiliki beberapa sumber informasi tambahan."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:27
msgid ""
"OpenShot has several `YouTube Tutorials <https://www.youtube.com/playlist?"
"list=PLymupH2aoNQNezYzv2lhSwvoyZgLp1Q0T>`_ available to help you learn more."
msgstr ""
"OpenShot memiliki beberapa `Tutorial YouTube <https://www.youtube.com/"
"playlist?list=PLymupH2aoNQNezYzv2lhSwvoyZgLp1Q0T>`_ yang tersedia untuk "
"membantu Anda belajar lebih banyak."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:28
msgid ""
"OpenShot has a `Reddit User Community <https://openshot.org/forum>`_ "
"dedicated to users helping users, answering questions, and discussing video "
"editing and OpenShot topics."
msgstr ""
"OpenShot memiliki `Komunitas Pengguna Reddit <https://openshot.org/forum>`_ "
"yang didedikasikan untuk pengguna saling membantu, menjawab pertanyaan, dan "
"mendiskusikan pengeditan video serta topik OpenShot."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:29
msgid ""
"If you would like to help improve this User Guide, `view source on GitHub "
"<https://github.com/OpenShot/openshot-qt/tree/develop/doc>`_."
msgstr ""
"Jika Anda ingin membantu meningkatkan Panduan Pengguna ini, `lihat sumber di "
"GitHub <https://github.com/OpenShot/openshot-qt/tree/develop/doc>`_."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:30
msgid ""
"If you have discovered a new bug, please `Report a Bug <https://www.openshot."
"org/issues/new/>`_."
msgstr ""
"Jika Anda menemukan bug baru, silakan `Laporkan Bug <https://www.openshot."
"org/issues/new/>`_."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:31
msgid ""
"If you need professional support, you can open a ticket by sending an "
"message to support@openshot.org or `Schedule a call <https://calendly.com/"
"openshot-support/desktop>`_."
msgstr ""
"Jika Anda membutuhkan dukungan profesional, Anda dapat membuka tiket dengan "
"mengirim pesan ke support@openshot.org atau `Jadwalkan panggilan <https://"
"calendly.com/openshot-support/desktop>`_."
